{"tid":1738857,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣撚入] 建立黃色經濟圈文宣區","createTime":"2019-11-19T11:17:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T16:51:07.000Z","uid":27754,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dd8785574f6a2383354240eaa608b9984278af9e","tid":1738857,"uid":27754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:17:01.000Z","msg":"就無國界醫生都跪一事，我諗緊唔知呢條橋work唔work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n與其我地日日痴文宣比人搣，我地可否整文宣派比鋪頭商户，由我地本身重點懲罰黃店，變成標籤非黃店既鋪頭<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>理撚得佢藍定黃，無貼文宣就唔幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n就好似之前搞個d有營食肆，正品正貨商戶，caring company 咁<br />\n<br />\n實際做法係先用文宣FB, IG，TG煲幾日<br />\n舉例由12月1號開始，市民不再幫襯無文宣既鋪頭，<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">當生意額下降，唔夠隔離爭，佢地就會驚，好似依家個個都想認證做黄店咁</span></span></span></span>，當直至佢地有第一張文宣開始，文宣組就可以行動不斷供新野比佢地<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">咁樣鋪頭為左加入黃色經濟圈，就算藍既都會跪</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，其次本身消費者，食客都會好似睇得CCTVB多咁，潛移默化加入我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，再者又可以恢復返市場既平衡，唔洗李嘉誠拎光環，藍絲食環又唔敢隨便撕私人地方既野，大家話work唔work?<br />\n<br />\n如果有連鎖集團加入做呢件事，個影響力應該會仲大<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">讓文宣組一齊加入經濟戰！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b1f65bce1dd04bab0b8bec1c3d3dc461f6f2b11e","tid":1738857,"uid":27754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:18:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"703c45d616b9b020b9fc9b4893a01215189cdf55","tid":1738857,"uid":27754,"like":